            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-2"></div>
                <div class="col-8 lead jumbotron float-center" id="textbox" style="padding:2%;border:2px solid black;">
                    A template for the PIP Server is a text file that has ISIS3 data keys or names inside
                    the actual figure description. The server reads in the tpl file and exchanges all the data keys with the
                    actual data values from the ISIS3 header. 
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class=" col-5 jumbotron float-center" id="textbox" 
